{"tid":1554331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如記者開返個記招講下點比黑警攻擊、侮辱同誤導，一定好撚震憾！","createTime":"2019-09-09T02:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T03:02:19.000Z","uid":36592,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd4dba2d4e51483c9b0a8d75ebf448770f31407","tid":1554331,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"與其黎黎去去都係等記協出D無用既聲明譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如記者開個記招，搵記者（香港外國都要）講返點比黑警攻擊、侮辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲可以講埋每日四點狡辯會黑警點樣誤導公眾，用你哋既報導同fact check翻黑警舊帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港市民一定支持記者保障自己人身安全，新聞自由同公眾知情權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時記得請埋江狗同謝狗，比佢地任問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持記者為自己為公眾發聲請正評及推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25efffc3bdaaa43cc806d383f41c821623e133a7","tid":1554331,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"請各位注意推埋呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【點解無人講】有醫生上港台證實私刑：手足被打頭，打斷牙，醫院被黑警監控<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553742</a>"},{"pid":"e53a9029730f77c5737f77f2d48ff49be9118055","tid":1554331,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:30:30.000Z","msg":"記協囉"},{"pid":"a6d80414327f23f0e5e268d39c9b924eca6fdbd2","tid":1554331,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:30:32.000Z","msg":"黑警惡行全集英文版, 請用盡一切方法廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9qD0StPLq6M&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9qD0StPLq6M%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&